name: Titli Trust
description: They supports the Society in its alternate livelihoods program supporting EcoTourism and bee-keeping. And also supports the Society in the Rural Schools Conservation Education Program.

name: Uttarakhand Forest Department -Mussoorie Forest Division
description: They supports the Society in its conservation education program, programs during Wildlife Week and tree plantation.

name: Uttarakhand Forest Department -Ecotourism Wing
description: They supports the development of ecotourism in Devalsari through training capability building and its village development program for rural tourism.

name: Been There Doon That
description: BTDT supports the society in its conservation and livelihood programs supporting its activities for heritage and nature ecotourism, organic food produce and bee-keeping.

name: ONGC
description: ONGC has funded the Devalsari Society in its bee-keeping project in Corbett landscape. And is funding Titli Trust in its Devalsari Ecotourism Development Project.
